
<h2>Users</h2>
Total Number of Users: <strong><em> <%= @total_users %> </strong></em> users. <br>
Most Active User: <strong><em> <%= @most_active.username%></strong></em> with <%= @most_active.posts.count %> posts.<br>
Least Active User: <strong><em> <%= @least_active.username%></strong></em> with <%= @least_active.posts.count %> posts.<br>
Newest User: <strong><em> <%= @newest_user.username%></strong></em> created on <%= @newest_user.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y.")%> <br>
Oldest User: <strong><em> <%= @oldest_user.username%></strong></em> created on <%= @oldest_user.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y.")%> <br>
User With The Most Followers: <strong><em><%= @most_followers.username%> </strong></em> with <%= @most_followers.followers.count%> followers.<br>
User With The Least Followers: <strong><em> <%= @least_followers.username%></strong></em> with <%= @least_followers.followers.count%> followers.<br> 


<h2>Communities</h2>
