Least Active Community: <strong><em> <%= @least_active_community.name%></strong></em> with <%= @least_active_community.posts.count %> posts.<br>
Newest Community: <strong><em> <%= @newest_community.name%></strong></em> created on <%= @newest_community.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y.")%> <br>
Oldest Community: <strong><em> <%= @oldest_community.name%></strong></em> created on <%= @oldest_community.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y.")%> <br>

<h2>Posts</h2>
Total Number of Posts: <strong><em> <%= @total_posts %> </strong></em> posts. <br>
Newest Post: <strong><em> <%= @newest_post.name%></strong></em> created on <%= @newest_post.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y.")%> <br>
Oldest Post: <strong><em> <%= @oldest_post.name%></strong></em> created on <%= @oldest_post.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y.")%> <br>
Longest Post: <strong><em> <%= @longest_post.name%></strong></em><br>
